<div class="title">A Journey to the Other Side</div>
<div class="substance">Clonazepam, Diazepam, Zolpidem & Diphenhydramine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Tyler+S&Exact=1">Tyler S</a></div>


